==English==
===Phrasal verb===
'''to [[reinvent]] the [[wheel]]''' ('''reinvents the wheel''', '''reinventing the wheel''', '''reinvented the wheel''')

#{{idiom}} To [[redo]] [[work]] [[unnecessary|unneccessarily]] when it has already been done [[satisfactory|satisfactorily]]; to [[rethink]] a working system, technique, etc. in a pointless attempt to improve it.
#:''Just use the database as it is and don't try to '''reinvent the wheel'''.''

